# Frontend static UI

## Structure

- Pages: `frontend/*.html` — shell via `shared-sidebar.js`, `shell-drawer.js`.
- Shared JS: `frontend/js/` — one concern per file.
- Marketing copy: `frontend/js/marketing-copy.js`, `docs/copy-seo-spec.md`.
- API base: `frontend/js/api-base.js` — never hardcode production URLs in pages.

## Safety

- Use `frontend/js/html-safe.js` for API-sourced strings in `innerHTML`.
- Prefer `textContent` over raw HTML interpolation.

## Auth

- Session: `auth-stack.js`, `session-user-hydrate.js`, `session-chrome-pre.js`.

## Lint & test

- Inline lint: `python run_tests.py frontend-lint`.
- E2E page loads: `tests/e2e/test_pages_load.py`.

## Deploy

- Frontend ships to separate repo via `uploadm8-frontend-push` skill — not bundled in backend push.
